{"tid":1606280,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"聽日你地千期唔好咁有目標，直接燒政府建築同警署呀","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T01:36:30.000Z","uid":161430,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"57535d5c950787f36f9fa8c32ab98e4d624006c4","tid":1606280,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:53:54.000Z","msg":"我覺得好似之前咁圍警署先好，一係喺屋企張床最安全<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好直接燒呀，咁樣d警察反應唔切</span>，<br />\n你地又唔係圍，而係燒完快快手又即刻走左去，<br />\n咁好唔負責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣真係會搞到人<br />\n<br />\n政府建築又係，最多圍下好喇，<br />\n唔好直接打爆佢同埋燒，太危險<br />\n<br />\n聽日直播見啦"},{"pid":"8479b69273e385d732bbd892dc3978cda36af483","tid":1606280,"uid":150267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:54:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">三點燒黨旗</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">［主線］<span style=\"color: red;\">聽日一定要做啲有標誌性嘅</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1604870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1604870</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武 和理非入<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\"> 依到有合集帶啲咩</span></strong><br />\n［整合］<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一執齊野</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603888</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">無豬咀就帶定條濕毛巾cover 口同鼻 <br />\n會好啲</span><br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好行甘前</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">仲有巴打目標post<br />\n十一國殤　六區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600404\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600404</a></span>"},{"pid":"209cabdadfc9b2b1c81eaa1f6f061e7bad7637a0","tid":1606280,"uid":161430,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www8.gocar2.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/TEMPTEMP-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5%B7%B2%E4%BF%AE%E5%BE%A9-%E5